{"id":"index.html","dependencies":[{"name":"./main.scss","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/main.scss","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"./static/pics/Artboard 1.jpg","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/static/pics/Artboard 1.jpg","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"./static/pics/house.png","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/static/pics/house.png","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"./static/pics/wandhama-bodies.jpg","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/static/pics/wandhama-bodies.jpg","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"./wandhama.js","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/wandhama.js","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"_css_loader","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html","resolved":"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/parcel-bundler/src/builtins/css-loader.js"},{"name":"/Users/u6075477/projects/.babelrc","includedInParent":true,"mtime":1556862282399},{"name":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/package.json","includedInParent":true,"mtime":1610182172116}],"generated":{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Document</title>\n  <link href=\"/cbe08353cc4beeaa4203d86039afc03c.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=PT+Serif&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <div class=\"top slide\">\n    <h1 class=\"headline\">A nightmare revisited</h1>\n    <p class=\"subhed\">Reliving the Wandhama massacre of 1998. </p>\n    <div class=\"go-down bounce\"><i class=\"icon-down-open\"></i></div>\n  </div>\n\n\n  <div id=\"text-map\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      Wandhama is a quiet village in central Kashmir’s Ganderbal district. The name in Kashmiri means ‘hot in winter’\n      i.e. providing comfort to its people.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"wandhama-locator\">\n      <img src=\"/8856da450dc8ce4133cd5b6e1eeb7e1c.jpg\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n\n  <div id=\"text-map\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      But on 25th January 1998, Wandhama failed to live upto it's name.\n      It witnessed the killing of 23 Kashmiri Hindus in the dead of the night by unidentified gunmen.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- the gunmen came to their house dressed like Indian Army soldiers, had tea with them, waiting for a radio message indicating that all Hindu families in the village had been covered. After a brief conversation they rounded up all the members of the Hindu households and then summarily gunned them down with Kalashnikov rifles.[8] The massacre was allegedly committed under Abdul Hamid Gada of the Hizbul Mujahideen and was timed to coincide with the Shab-e-Qadar, the holiest night of the month of Ramzan, when believers stay awake until dawn.[9] Gada was subsequently shot dead by Indian security forces in 2000.[10] -->\n\n  <div id=\"text-solo\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      The events of that night are recalled by one of the survivors of the incident, a 14-year-old Hindu boy named Vinod\n      Kuman Dhar alias Ashu. The teenager had slipped away and hidden himself in a dark corner of the house.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"text-house\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      “The gunmen were dressed like Indian Army soldiers,”, Ashu said piecing the details together. “They had tea with\n      us, waiting for a radio message indicating that all pandit families in the village had been\n      covered.”\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"wandhama-house\">\n      <img src=\"/3f536d14e4c4ea8f0c46ace46f0255ee.png\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"text-bodies\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      After a brief conversation they rounded up all the members of the Hindu households and then gunned them down with\n      Kalashnikov rifles.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"wandhama-bodies\">\n      <img src=\"/d0aa8cc395c042d0eff543a81a4b3e10.jpg\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"text-victims\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      There was burning smell of the human flesh everywhere. A mother had unsuccessfully tried to save her infant by\n      hiding him in her lap but both got killed together. The cop trying to separate them couldn’t.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"text-stay\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      The neighbourhood had changed forever. Those killed that night had chosen to stay in the valley despite the fact\n      that majority of their community members had migrated in 1990.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"text-victims\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      The victims included 10 men, 9 women and 4 children.\n      <span style=\"margin-top: 20px; display: block;\">These are their stories.</span>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n\n\n\n  <!-- <div id=\"text-3\" class=\"slide text-slide\">\n    <p>\n      Lone survivor, a 12-year-old boy, Vinod Kumar aka Ashu, the locals said that he had miraculously escaped as he hid\n      himself under a pack of heavy straw nearby to his home.\n    </p>\n  </div> -->\n\n  <div id=\"photos\" class=\"slide\">\n    <div class=\"photo-row row-1\">\n      <p class=\"family-name\">Bhatt Family</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"photo-row row-2\">\n      <p class=\"family-name\">Koul Family</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"photo-row row-3\">\n      <p class=\"family-name\">Lal family</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"photo-row row-4\">\n      <p class=\"family-name\">Nath family</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pic-description\">\n      <p class=\"name\"></p>\n      <p class=\"age\"></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</body>\n\n<script src=\"/ca536e47f3f828a66947fddf7b1dc418.js\"></script>\n\n</html>"},"sourceMaps":null,"error":null,"hash":"1d2b65c65e3bd0c6d0c26224de399a99","cacheData":{"env":{}}}